headline: Gen Z Is Streaming Through The Workday — 84% Say It Boosts Focus, While Half Admit They've Delayed Tasks To Finish A Show
summary: Gen Z employees often stream TV shows or movies during the workday, with 84 % saying it helps them focus, according to a recent Tubi–Harris Poll survey. The survey found that more than half, 53%, slowed assignments to finish an episode, and 48% admitted to lying to supervisors about their on-screen habits.
